rows.label: qst701911_msg0001
rows.name:
What was her name? Maquia? We need
a skilled helmswoman like her.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0101
rows.name: The six of them went to Invidia.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0102
rows.name:
I do hope they can pull it off and
come back with the Dragon Incense.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0103
rows.name:
While we're waiting, feel free
to get on with whatever tasks you
have going on at the moment.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0104
rows.name:
Or even take a break.
It won't kill you.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0201
rows.name:
I was very pleased to hear that the
squad accomplished their mission.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0202
rows.name:
Now take the Dragon Incense to
little Freja-san, and make this
whole endeavor worth the trouble.
